<html>
  <head>
    <title>Password Changed - Shopwise</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; background-color:
      #f5f5f5; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .logo { width: 150px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;
      } .header { text-align: center; background-color: #f3f3f3; padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; } .header h1 { color: #333333; margin: 0;
      padding: 0; } .content { padding: 20px; } .footer { text-align: center;
      background-color: #f3f3f3; padding: 10px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
      .footer p { margin: 0; padding: 0; } .button { display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #ffffff;
      background-color: #3498db; border-radius: 5px; } .button:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <img
          class="logo"
          src="{{logoUrl}}"
          alt="Shopwise Logo"
          width="150"
          style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Password Changed</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello, {{name}}</p>
        <p>This is to inform you that the password for your Shopwise account has
          recently been changed. If you didn't make this change, please contact
          us immediately for further assistance.</p>
        <p>If you made the change, you can ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br />Shopwise Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>